Advent o Code
=============

Advent of code is a collection of programming puzzles created by Eric Wastl.
These puzzles can be solved in any programming language.

I recently came across advent of code and the puzzles really piqued my interest. I decided to solve these puzzles and share my solutions to the world. I enjoy solving questions like these and it's fun!

My solutions might not be the best ones out there, but still, I'm going to share them with the world.

I am going to solve these questions one at a time, program the solution by hand, in my free time. Looking forward to completing all the puzzles!